A member of the Inn League seems to have landed drunk in a sty in Budgeford, where everyone can see him. Shameful!

What a disgrace. Dod Rumble is dead drunk, right in the middle of town!

You should make sure Dod Rumble gets out of sight before people start getting offended by his public display of drunkenness.
Dod Rumble is the disgrace of Budgford. Even the pigs behave better!\n\nYou should escort the drunken hobbit to a secluded place where he won't be disturbing the good-mannered folk around town.
